Package: ARID
Title: Atacama Repository of Isotopic Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Diego", "Mayorga", , "mayorgarmijo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An open, collaborative repository of isotopic data for the
    Atacama Desert of northern Chile. Provides tools to access, filter,
    and visualize stable isotope data integrated with contextual,
    geographical, chronological, and bibliographic variables.
